---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Programmatic SEO Directory Websites" description="Build programmatic SEO directory websites with scalable templates, clean internal linking, and indexation-safe architecture.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="text-sm text-[#00f0ff] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-wider">PROGRAMMATIC SEO</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mt-4 mb-5 font-['Space_Grotesk']">Programmatic SEO Directory Websites</h1>
      <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] text-lg max-w-3xl">I design pSEO-ready directory systems with template-level quality controls, clean URL architecture, and internal linking that supports indexation instead of bloating crawl budget.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5"><p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Template Depth</p><p class="text-white text-2xl font-['JetBrains_Mono'] mt-1">3-5 Types</p></div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5"><p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Indexation Focus</p><p class="text-white mt-1">Quality > URL volume</p></div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5"><p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Use Case</p><p class="text-white mt-1">City/category scale pages</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">What gets implemented</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]">
          <li>• pSEO template system (city, category, city+category)</li>
          <li>• Programmatic metadata structure</li>
          <li>• Canonical/noindex controls for duplication risk</li>
          <li>• Internal link modules for crawl pathways</li>
          <li>• Sitemap strategy and indexing sanity checks</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">Why this matters</h2>
        <p class="text-[#8b8b9a]">Programmatic SEO fails when pages are thin or repetitive. The goal is not just generating URLs, but building templates that satisfy real search intent and can earn stable rankings over time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0a0a0f] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00f0ff] to-[#00c8ff] rounded-xl">See pSEO-ready plans</a>
      <a href="/case-studies/indoorclimbinggym" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl">See pSEO case study</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
